Subject: [PATCH 2/5] Add fix mc/sites: lattice-gas GCMC on a frozen site
 catalogue

gc + source modes; catalogue = empty sites (compute or static file) +
occupied entries (species atoms); synchronized RanPark proposals and
lattice-gas acceptance min(1,exp(-beta(dU-/+mu))) on all ranks, owner
executes; full-energy dU (gcmc pattern) with upstream ENERGY_ONLY hint
+ GRACE compute_energy_only extract hook; real-delete trial with exact
pack/unpack_exchange restore on reject; equal-style Temp/mu variables;
tfac_insert/charge/maxspecies/overlap_cutoff keywords; restart of RNG
state + counters; 8-slot output vector.

