+/* ----------------------------------------------------------------------
+   Contributing author: Erik Bitzek (erik.bitzek@googlemail.com)
+
+   Lattice-gas grand-canonical (and fixed-rate source) Monte Carlo on a
+   frozen per-block catalogue of geometry-derived sites, for hybrid MD/MC.
+   Empty sites come from a sites-producing compute (e.g. sites/voronoi) or
+   a static file; occupied sites are the current species atoms themselves.
+   Move mechanics follow fix gcmc (synchronized RanPark proposals and
+   acceptance on all ranks, owning rank executes, collective full-energy
+   evaluation); the acceptance is the lattice-gas convention
+   min(1, exp(-beta*(dU -/+ mu))) with the fix's own mu reference (no
+   ideal-gas factors).
+------------------------------------------------------------------------- */
